column5: Hey Folks,  Just put up a new report on my site - "A Walk in the Woods." An afternoon hunkered down in a cornfield trying to photograph deer. Feel free to check it out:   http://justinhoffmanoutdoors.com/2011/11/25/a-walk-in-the-woods/         Enjoy the report and pics...  Good Fishing,  Justin
Thats some real nice shots , Thanks for sharing .
That would made for good hunting.
sharp, clear pictures, looking at them makes you feel as if you are there
Thanks for the comments, guys. Back out again this week...here's hoping the big 8-pointer gets within camera range   One more day of Quebec bassin' on the scheds for tomorrow!  Good Fishing,  Justin
